The examples in this directory are modifications from the following repository:
https://github.com/repaper/gratis.git

Be sure to install the appropriate drivers as per the instructions at:
https://learn.adafruit.com/repaper-eink-development-board-arm-linux-raspberry-pi-beagle-bone-black/overview

You can find more information about the RePaper display here:
http://repaper.org
http://www.pervasivedisplays.com/

The LoremPixel script gets images from http://lorempixel.com.
